{"tid":595859,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唱國歌五音不全都犯法？茶記播國歌舉中指即瀨嘢！","createTime":"2018-03-17T05:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T06:10:20.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"92ff2b2b1adef5288e9e8b3a1b168c97c9172246","tid":595859,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180317/large/1521217078_6d1a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180317%2Flarge%2F1521217078_6d1a.png&h=e0a1584b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 政制及內地事務局提交的《國歌條例草案》寫明，任何人公開及故意篡改國歌歌詞、曲譜，或以歪曲、貶損方式奏唱國歌，均屬犯罪。政府消息人士指出，執法的重點在於「公開、故意」，假設在球場內奏唱國歌時，有人非公開、非故意地「清喉嚨」而發出噓聲，就不構成不尊重；另外，奏唱國歌時如普通話欠佳、五音不全，只要並非公開及故意，亦不會有刑責。<br />\n<br />\n政府消息人士針對不同奏唱國歌的情境作出回應，除球場噓國歌情境，不少市民擔心一旦立法，是否將來在所有場合，只要聽到國歌就要馬上肅立，否則即墮法網；政府消息人士指出，執法重點在於不肅立的行為是否故意及有否貶損國歌，又指相關條文針對的「唔係路過嗰啲（人）」；又舉例指，若在茶餐廳用膳時突然聽到電視播國歌毋須肅立，但若播歌時舉中指就很大機會犯法。<br />\n<br />\n此外，如果有人在網上發佈貶損國歌的內容，政府消息人士指出，網絡世界一般會理解為公開場合，因此在網上發佈相關言論同樣屬於違法。消息人士亦明言不應該將國歌用作二次創作、不應該藉國歌表達對於政治問題的不滿，「即使好熱愛祖國，都可以有其他方式表達，擔心就無謂走去試」，或者創作後「唔好喺網上分享」，如果想表達政治上的不滿可以叫口號、舉橫額，毋須牽涉國歌。<br />\n<br />\n記者 呂浩然 周婷<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180317/57957724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57957724&d=fZM7N6QrlwatQABWD2VYMzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=4a857c56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180317%2F57957724&h=1a6fae9f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180317/57957724</a>"},{"pid":"140265c10df4839b21a3015d3b40017bb90eede0","tid":595859,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:57:44.000Z","msg":"吹蕭安唔洗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cab667df90be3012b35acef6b3c90cc18c82279","tid":595859,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T05:58:28.000Z","msg":"叫古天樂唱即拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9548f0236aea621ac1a901745c7cbb215a571fe","tid":595859,"uid":147367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:00:42.000Z","msg":"算鳩數啦，故意既龍門咪又係隨意搬，變相23條姐"},{"pid":"9abf1a4cadfbf521e9daf8f9acdcf91ca5f75efb","tid":595859,"uid":68080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:03:08.000Z","msg":"手機儲存住国歌<br />\n邊條友鬧人 舉中指 <br />\n即刻播国歌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"342c8ef0c95fa0d97f04ea61a30f167dd131dfcf","tid":595859,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:03:24.000Z","msg":"點知係咪故意走音"},{"pid":"321c71259d9920baeb992005d6d0a1dc5a72c15f","tid":595859,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:04:44.000Z","msg":"「即使好熱愛祖國，都可以有其他方式表達，擔心就無謂走去試」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n依家就係冇人鍾意支那"},{"pid":"06dccfd8768901b935318f4b715eb9368df2b1d0","tid":595859,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 執法者擁有絕對權力"},{"pid":"912bb400322717283980b773462079d75e32c71a","tid":595859,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T06:07:36.000Z","msg":"茶記伙記捉到播國歌舉中指食客<br />\n可獲舉報獎金$5000，實行全民紅衛兵"},{"pid":"dc82573029881b53490c4b71dc2fad3cba303883","tid":595859,"uid":40763